<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p> She's a member of one of the world's biggest girl bands.</p>

<p>And Perrie Edwards, 27, proved she has all the makings for the job as she showcased her natural beauty in a dazzling headshot posted to Instagram on Saturday.</p>

<p>The Shout Out To My Ex singer stared intensely over her shoulder in the photo, where she added a caption to note she had 'caught the right light'.</p>

<p>Natural beauty: Perrie Edwards dazzled fans with her grey-eyed stare in this headshot posted to Instagram on Saturday</p>

<p>She wore minimal make-up, with jet black mascara around her eyes but only a hint of foundation and lip gloss to best showcase her natural beauty.</p>

<p>The Little Mix singer's chin rested on her bare shoulder with her lips pursed open provocatively, for the ultimate beach babe look. </p>

<p>She accessorised for the snap with a number of ear-lobe and cartilage piercings, while her flaxen tresses hangs loosely in waves over her shoulders. </p>

<p>Perrie alluringly captioned the post: 'Tried to find the light, it found me first...'.  </p>

<p>Bubbly: The singer also recently shared a shot of her in the dramatic headdress she wears in the video for Little Mix's latest single, Holiday</p>

<p>Happy couple: Perrie is back at work after enjoying a relaxing summer with beau of three years, footballer Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain</p>

<p>Little Mix - which includes Perrie and bandmates Leigh-Anne Pinnock, 28, Jade Thirlwall, 27, and Jesy Nelson, 29 - are set to release their sixth album, Confetti, on 6th November. </p>

<p>The band released a video for their latest single Holiday last month, in which Perrie accessorises in a stunning bubble-inspired headpiece that she recently shared a snap of with her fans.</p>

<p>The band shared the front cover of their new album on Instagram for the first time on Wednesday. </p>

<p>The girls looked sensational as they posed up a storm wearing only glitter on their faces in the sizzling new artwork. </p>

<p>Sensational: The band shared the front cover of their new album Confetti for the first time on Instagram on Wednesday</p>

<p>Sharing the snap, they wrote: 'So much love, emotion and energy has gone into the making of this record and now the news is out we can finally get excited about it with you!!'</p>

<p>Little Mix's previous albums are DNA, Salute, Get Weird, Glory Days and their most recent offering LM5 in 2018.</p>

<p>The band's recent recent publicity push will be a welcome change for Perrie, after she was forced to spend much of August in quarantine following a trip to Ibiza due with boyfriend Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain. </p>

<p>The couple made their relationship Instagram official in January 2017 and spent all of lockdown together. </p>

<p>Well-established: Little Mix's five previous albums are DNA, Salute, Get Weird, Glory Days and their most recent offering LM5, which was released in 2018</p>
